commit.message:
Prepare Release 4.1.0_rc0

Signed-off-by: Andreas Fuchs <andreas.fuchs@infineon.com>

unit tests:  skip tests which fail on 32-bit with _FILE_BITS=64

Tests file the unit tests are compiled with _FILE_BITS is set to 64.
The tests work without problems if _FILE_BITS is not set.
Addresses: #2786

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

maintainers: Update the maintainer file.

The pgp fingerprint for the maintainers is added.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

CI: fix error in tests with sanitizer error on github.

To fix this error "run: sudo sysctl vm.mmap_rnd_bits=28" is temporally
added to ./github/workflow/main.yml
Addresses: #2792

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

esys-test: skip test esys-pcr-auth-value.

Test is skipped if setting of an auth value is not allowed for a pcrNum.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix warnings unused variable.

* In ifapi_json_TPMS_POLICYAUTHORIZE_serialize it has to be checked
  whether the number of an optional condition is greater zero.
* A warning "unused variable" if LOG_LEVEL == 0 is fixed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix cleanup of policy sessions.

Policy sessions were not flushed if the policy session
was successfully executed but the command where the policy
was used for authorization was executed with an error.
For the session cleanup in error cases it will be tested
whethe the policy session still exists in the TPM.
Fixes: #2784

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix possible null pointer access in fapi crypto.

* In the cleanup function for an ossl hash context the variables
  were not checked before calling the ossl cleanup functions.
* An unneded cast was removed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix possible out of bound array access in IMA parser.

The wrong size variable was used to check the out of bound access.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix error checking authorization of signing key.

The return code of the authorization function for a signing key was not
checked.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

TCTI device: Fix possible unmarshalling from uninitialized variable.

Ther was no else case in the receive function when the header
was not received but afterwards the partial_size was unmarshalled
from header. Now TSS2_TCTI_RC_GENERAL_FAILURE is returned in
this case.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix possible out of bound array access in IMA parser.

The IMA parser did not check the length field for the ima type.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: fix memset 0 in ifapi_json_TPMS_POLICYNV_deserialize.

The wrong size was used to clear the memory if the field was not found.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Add fclose in error cases.

The function file_to_buffer did not close fp in error cases.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Add size check for reading ima header.

It's now checked whether the complete ima header is read.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: fix dead code in ima set ff digest.

Returns were exchanged with goto error.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: fix memcopy of hmac digest.

As destination field now sha512 instead of sha1 is used.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix wrong usage of local variable in provisioning.

The variable int_ca_file was used after return_try_again.
Now the value of the corresponding environment variable is used.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

TCTI SWTPM: Check return value of read from socket.

The possible return value -1 is now checked.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Remove dead code in fapi_uti.c

A falltrhough which can't be reached is removed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

ESYS: fix unchecked return value in esys crypto.

A return value was not assigned but checked afterwards.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

ESYS: Fix leak in Esys_TR_FromTPMPublic.

In an error case the variables public, name, and qualifiedName were
not freed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: remove dead code in fapi provisioning.

A fallthrough after a return is removed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix leak in IMA digest check.

The crypto context is now freed in error cases.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

SYS: Fix size check in Tss2_Sys_GetCapability.

The size of the size field was added to the buffer size.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

FAPI: Fix leak if an openssl error occurs.

If and error does occur in the openssl crypto functions
the context is not freed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

TCTI: remove dead code in tcti-spi-helper.c

Duplicate statement is removed.

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

ESYS: Remove dead code in esys change auth functions

Dead code is removed in Esys_NV_ChangeAuth.c and Esys_ObjectChangeAuth.c

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

TEST: Fix test with ESYS and FAPI disabled.

The functions needed for ESYS anf FAPI test are activated with
an ifdef now.
Fixes: #2770

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>

configure.ac Check json-c version.

tss does not support json-c versions < 0.13. The version is now
checked by configure.
Addresses #2767

Signed-off-by: Juergen Repp <juergen_repp@web.de>
